WBP,Systems,Torch,is,a,project,management,service,that,allows,users,to,bid,collaborate,track,resources,and,invoice,Using,the,API,allows,clients,to,interact,with,Torch,programmatically,Torch,s,API,is,an,XML,based,conversion,between,the,programs,Every,request,is,sent,in,XML,every,response,will,be,in,XML